response.overview: In a rural northern community, a creatures born of radioactive fallout has developed a taste for the locals. After the discovery of multiple victims, local sheriff Bob Jenson calls in game warden Joe Miller to help identify the creature responsible. With the help of local guide Elaine Skogland they set out into the wilderness in order to put a stop to the beast one way or another.
response.title: Beast of the Northwoods
